      <TwoColumnLayout
        title="Concept of Brand Logo Display"
        linkUrl="/en/guidelines/gl_ab_inportance_en.html"
        linkText="The Importance of Our Brand"
      >
        <div class="content">
          <p>
            The Panasonic brand represents a bond with customers developed through a variety of activities promoted by all employees. It is an important and irreplaceable asset created through strenuous efforts over the years.
          </p>
          <p>
            Brand displays in accordance with the rules are an important factor for protecting the trust in Panasonic and its brand value.
          </p>
        </div>
      </TwoColumnLayout>

      <TwoColumnLayout
        title="The Basic Principles for Brand Display"
        linkUrl="/en/guidelines/gl_bp_concept_disp_en.html"
        linkText="Basic Principles for Brand Display"
      >
        <div class="content">
          <h3>The Basic Principles for Brand Display are established with emphasis on originality, legality, and visibility.</h3>
          <div class="white_box">
            <div class="text_row">
              <div class="text_head">
                <h4>Originality:</h4>
              </div>
              <div class="text_body">
                <p>
                  Ensure to always display the brand logo independently and maintain consistency.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="text_row">
              <div class="text_head">
                <h4>Legality:</h4>
              </div>
              <div class="text_body">
                <p>
                  Ensure to properly secure and assert our own rights, do not infringe on the rights of other companies, and respect their rights.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="text_row">
              <div class="text_head">
                <h4>Visibility:</h4>
              </div>
              <div class="text_body">
                <p>
                  Avoid situations where the logo cannot be recognized due to its size or color or lacks clarity.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </TwoColumnLayout>
    </div>
  </section>
